        WHAT_YOU_WANT_TO_EXPLORE_THE_TOWERS_OF                                  = 8753,  -- What, you want to explore the towers of Pso'Xja? That shouldn't be a problem. We recently opened those ruins to all explorers.
        HOWEVER_THE_TENSHODO_IS_CURRENTLY_CONDUCTING_AN_INVESTIGATION           = 8754,  -- However, the Tenshodo is currently conducting an investigation on the deeper areas of the central tower, and we can't have pesky adventurers running around getting in our way.
