        HAIL_SOLDIER_I_AM_A_PURVEYOR_TASKED_WITH                                = 10227,  -- Hail, soldier. I am a purveyor tasked with furnishing the brave men and women of the Voidwatch with essential supplies. My wares can be yours, provided you've got [Conquest Points/Imperial Standing/Allied Notes] to trade. After all, we can't afford to let our limited resources go to waste in the hands of some unproven rookie.
        PROCURE_SUPPLIES_NOT_NOW                                                = 10228,  -- Procure supplies? ([Points/Standing/Notes]: #) Not now. % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#). % (#).
        HOW_MANY_NONE_ACTUALLY_ONE_COST_THREE_COST                              = 10229,  -- How many? ([Points/Standing/Notes]: #) None, actually. One (Cost: #). Three (Cost: #), Six (Cost: #). Nine (Cost: #). Twelve (Cost: #).
        THIS_WILL_COST_YOU                                                      = 10230,  -- This % will cost you # [Conquest Points/credits of Imperial Standing/Allied Notes].
        IT_SEEMS_YOU_RE_SHORT_ON_SOLDIER_COME                                   = 10231,  -- It seems you're short on [Conquest Points/Imperial Standing credits/Allied Notes], soldier. Come back when you've got a bit more seasoning under your belt.
        PROCEED_REQUIRED_YES_NO                                                 = 10232,  -- Proceed? (Required [Points/Standing/Notes]: #) Yes. No.
        OBTAINS_IN_EXCHANGE_FOR                                                 = 10233,  -- % obtains % in exchange for # [Conquest Points/credits of Imperial Standing/Allied Notes].
        OBTAINS_IN_EXCHANGE_FOR_2                                               = 10234,  -- % obtains # % in exchange for # [Conquest Points/credits of Imperial Standing/Allied Notes].
        OBTAINS_IN_EXCHANGE_FOR_3                                               = 10235,  -- % obtains % in exchange for # [Conquest Points/credits of Imperial Standing/Allied Notes].
        THIS_WILL_COST_YOU_2                                                    = 10236,  -- This % will cost you # [Conquest Points/credits of Imperial Standing/Allied Notes].
        YOU_ALREADY_HAVE_AND_I_M_NOT_AUTHORIZED                                 = 10237,  -- You already have %, and I'm not authorized to furnish you with another. Resources are in short supply. You'll have to make do with what you've already got.
        HOW_MANY                                                                = 10246,  -- How many? ( [Conquest Points/Imperial Standing/Allied Notes]: #)
        YOU_MAY_PURCHASE_UP_TO_AT_A_TIME                                        = 10247,  -- You may purchase up to # at a time.
        OH_WHAT_A_CRYING_WYING_SHAME_THE_CARDS                                  = 10248,  -- Oh, what a crying-wying shame! The cards open our eyes to the truth, yet so many still wander aimlessly through life, blind as batarus.
        BUT_IT_DOESN_T_HAVE_TO_BE_THIS                                          = 10249,  -- But it doesn't have to be this way! I just need someone to help me spread the wonders of fortune-wortune-telling across the land!
        I_PREDICT_THAT_IT_WOULD_BE_A_MOST                                       = 10250,  -- I predict that it would be a most fruitaruful career choice! What do you say?
        WHAT_DO_YOU_SAY_SURE_I_LL_HELP                                          = 10251,  -- What do you say? Sure, I'll help. Not today.
        I_SEE_DARK_CLOUDS_AND_STORMY_WORMY_SEAS                                 = 10252,  -- I see dark clouds and stormy-wormy seas on the horizon for he/she] who refuses to aid me! But oh well, it's your life...or death, as the case may be.
        OH_THANK_YOU_EVER_SO_MUCH_I_SEE                                         = 10253,  -- Oh, thank you ever so much! I see naughtaru but rainbows and rosy-woses in your future!
        I_M_SURE_YOU_ALREADY_KNOW_ABOUT_TARUT                                   = 10254,  -- I'm sure you already know about tarut cards, but let's not take any chances with such a vital-wital task, shall we?
        THERE_ARE_FOUR_TYPES_OF_CARDS_TO_WITARU                                 = 10255,  -- There are four types of cards. To witaru, we have the Hermit, the King, Death, and the Fool.
        THIS_MEANS_THAT_YOU_LL_END_UP_WITH                                      = 10256,  -- This means that you'll end up with an extra-wextra card, but no need to fretaru! You can give it to a friend, or simply toss it aside and spread the joy to a lucky anonymous passerby!
        GOT_ALL_THAT_THEN_OFF_YOU_GO                                            = 10257,  -- Got all that? Then off you go!
        I_M_NOT_IN_ANY_RUSH_BUT_SHOULD                                          = 10258,  -- I'm not in any rush, but should you find yourself shortaru on luck after a time, just come back here, okay? I'll see what I can do to turn your fortune-wortunes around.
        YOU_VE_DONE_MUCH_TO_SPREAD_TRUTH_AND                                    = 10259,  -- You've done much to spread truth and wisdom in Vana'diel today, my friend! Take this as a small token of my gratitude and come back whenever you need your fortune told. Ta-taru!
        OH_LOOK_WHO_S_BACK_RETURNED_TO_HELP                                     = 10260,  -- Oh, look who's back! Returned to help me spread the wonder of tarut cards across the realm, have you? I see not-insignificantaru rewards in the future of the generous adventurer who says yes!
        NO_DON_T_TELL_ME_I_SENSE_THIS                                           = 10261,  -- No, don't tell me...! I sense this hasn't been your lucky-wucky week.
        PERHAPS_A_NEW_SETARU_OF_CARDS_WILL_CHANGE                               = 10262,  -- Perhaps a new setaru of cards will change your fortunes. Here you go, and may fate smile upon you!
        HM_I_GOT_NO_BUSINESS_WITH_THE_LIKES                                     = 10263,  -- Hm? I got no business with the likes of you. Now get outta here.
        PSST_YOU_YEAH_YOU_I_GOT_A_SPECIAL                                       = 10264,  -- Psst, you. Yeah, you. I got a special deal for ya.
        FOR_A_NOMINAL_FEE_I_CAN_WARP_YA                                         = 10265,  -- For a nominal fee, I can warp ya to some outta-the-way battlefield entrances. No questions asked. Mind ya, I don't do this for just anyone, so ya'd better appreciate it.
        AS_FOR_GETTIN_BACK_YOU_RE_ON_YER                                        = 10266,  -- As for gettin' back, you're on yer own. I ain't runnin' a charity here, after all.
        WHERE_YA_HEADIN_TODAY_NOWHERE_GHELSBA_OUTPOST_HORLAIS                   = 10267,  -- Where ya headin' today? Nowhere. Ghelsba Outpost. Horlais Peak. Waughroon Shrine. Balga's Dais. Qu'Bia Arena.
        YA_SAY_THAT_LL_RUN_YA_GIL_WHADDAYA                                      = 10268,  -- [/Ghelsba Outpost/Horlais Peak/Waughroon Shrine/Balga's Dais/Qu'Bia Arena], ya say? That'll run ya # gil. Whaddaya say?
        WHADDAYA_SAY_CURRENT_GIL_PAY_AND_TELEPORT_ON                            = 10269,  -- Whaddaya say? (Current gil: #) Pay and teleport. On second thought...
        ALRIGHT_NOW_WE_JUST_GOTTA_PUT_THIS_BLINDFOLD                            = 10270,  -- Alright, now we just gotta put this blindfold on ya. A businessman's gotta protect his trade secrets, after all...
        THEN_WHADDAYA_WASTIN_MY_TIME_FOR_GET_LOST                               = 10271,  -- ...Then whaddaya wastin' my time for? Get lost!
        A_FINE_DAY_TO_YOU_GOOD_SIR_MADAM                                        = 10272,  -- A fine day to you, good sir/madam], and welcome to the Chamber of Commerce and Industry's Adoulin Pioneer Consultation Desk. How may I help you?
        WHAT_ASSISTANCE_DO_YOU_SEEK_YOU_KNOW_WHAT                               = 10273,  -- What assistance do you seek? You know what? Nevermind. I would like to apply. Tell me more about the system. Tell me more about the dungeons. I would like %. Do you have any work for me?
        SHOULD_YOU_HAVE_ANY_QUESTIONS_IN_THE_FUTURE                             = 10274,  -- Should you have any questions in the future, we would be pleased to assist you.
        THANK_YOU_FOR_YOUR_INTEREST_IN_OUR_PIONEER                              = 10275,  -- Thank you for your interest in our Pioneer Partnership Program.
        AS_PART_OF_THE_APPLICATION_PROCESS_YOU_WILL                             = 10276,  -- As part of the application process, you will need this %.
        TAKE_IT_WITH_YOU_AND_VISIT_ONE_OF                                       = 10277,  -- Take it with you and visit one of the dungeons from the list that I am about to give you. Which one you visit is your choice.
        OUR_SURVEY_STAFF_HAS_INSPECTED_EACH_OF_THE                              = 10278,  -- Our survey staff has inspected each of the areas in question and placed special markings at a particular location past the entrance.
        HOLD_UP_THE_I_HAVE_JUST_GIVEN_YOU                                       = 10279,  -- Hold up the % I have just given you and return it to me.
        AND_NOW_ALLOW_ME_TO_PRESENT_YOU_WITH                                    = 10280,  -- And now, allow me to present you with the list of applicable dungeons.
        IN_THE_REGION                                                           = 10281,  -- In the [Fauregandi/Ronfaure/Norvallen/Zulkheim/Gustaberg/Vollbow/Kolshushu/Aragoneu/Derfland/Sarutabaruta] region: [Ranguemont Pass/Yughott Grotto, King Ranperre's Tomb/Monastic Cavern, Eldieme Necropolis/Ordelle's Caves, Gusgen Mines/Dangruf Wadi, Korroloka Tunnel,/Gustav Tunnel/Labyrinth of Onzozo, Maze of Shakhrami/Garlaige Citadel/Crawlers' Nest/Outer Horutoto Ruins, Inner Horutoto Ruins,] [////Palborough Mines/////Toraimarai Canal]
        THIS_LIST_LOOKS_DAUNTING_TO_BE_SURE_BUT                                 = 10282,  -- This list looks daunting, to be sure, but we have faith that you will be able to complete this challenge.
        SOME_OF_THESE_MARKINGS_ARE_LOCATED_CLOSE_TO                             = 10283,  -- Some of these markings are located close to the entrance, while others are deep within.
        I_WISH_YOU_THE_BEST_OF_LUCK_IN                                          = 10284,  -- I wish you the best of luck in this endeavor.
        THE_GOVERNMENT_OF_JEUNO_HAS_PROMULGATED_A_SYSTEM                        = 10285,  -- The government of Jeuno has promulgated a system for adventurers to pioneer uncharted lands.
        THIS_SYSTEM_WAS_PROPOSED_BY_THE_LEADERS_OF                              = 10286,  -- This system was proposed by the leaders of the Sacred City of Adoulin, an overseas trading capital whose volume of trade rivals Jeuno's.
        PIONEERS_ARE_TO_TRAVERSE_THE_WATERS_OF_THE                              = 10287,  -- Pioneers are to traverse the waters of the Sea of Zafmlug, far to the west, and assist in colonizing the untamed wilds of Ulbuka.
        ONCE_WORD_OF_THIS_PROPOSAL_REACHED_SAN_D                                = 10288,  -- Once word of this proposal reached San d'Oria through various trade routes, it introduced Jeuno to the idea, which led to its eventual implementation.
        ADOULIN_IS_NOT_A_PLACE_FOR_THE_WEAK                                     = 10289,  -- Adoulin is not a place for the weak or uninitiated. Harsh wildlands surround the city, and simple layfolk stand no chance of surviving. It is due to these unique circumstances that Adoulin has begun recruiting highly seasoned adventurers to assist in seeing out its goals.
        HERE_AT_THE_CONSULTATION_DESK_WE_ISSUE_PERMITS                          = 10290,  -- Here at the Consultation Desk, we issue permits that allow proactive adventurers to cross over to Adoulin.
        HOWEVER_NEOPHYTES_CANNOT_PROVIDE_THE_SERVICES_ADOULIN_REQUIRES          = 10291,  -- However, neophytes cannot provide the services Adoulin requires. As such, the Chamber has commissioned a simple test for those seeking to make the perilous journey.
        THOSE_SEASONED_IN_BATTLE_SHOULD_FIND_IT_TO                              = 10292,  -- Those seasoned in battle should find it to be a relatively painless affair.
        ADOULIN_HAS_PREPARED_A_MULTITUDE_OF_OF_WHICH                            = 10293,  -- Adoulin has prepared a multitude of %, of which one will be given to each adventurer seeking to prove their worth.
        THESE_ARE_ATTUNED_TO_THE_LAND_AND_ARE                                   = 10294,  -- These % are attuned to the land, and are able to record markings located in specific locations. Further details will be provided once we have issued you the appropriate certifications.
        FOR_THE_TIME_BEING_LET_US_RETURN_TO                                     = 10295,  -- For the time being, let us return to the task you will have to face.
        BRING_THIS_OBJECT_WITH_YOU_AND_TAKE_IT                                  = 10296,  -- Bring this object with you and take it to one out of a list of several areas located throughout Vana'diel. Which place you choose to explore is for you to decide.
        YOU_MUST_SIMPLY_PASS_THE_OVER_THE_MARKINGS                              = 10297,  -- You must simply pass the % over the markings located in the area to finish your assignment.
        ONCE_YOU_HAVE_COMPLETED_THIS_TASK_SIMPLY_RETURN                         = 10298,  -- Once you have completed this task, simply return the % to us here and we will analyze the results.
        SHOULD_YOUR_TRIAL_BE_COMPLETED_APPROPRIATELY_YOU_WILL                   = 10299,  -- Should your trial be completed appropriately, you will be deemed to have passed, and will be issued %, enabling you to travel to Adoulin.
        THAT_SHOULD_CONSTITUTE_A_SUFFICIENT_EXPLANATION_SHOULD_YOU              = 10300,  -- That should constitute a sufficient explanation. Should you choose to undertake the test, I wish you the greatest of fortunes.
        AS_YOU_MAY_REMEMBER_THE_TEST_REQUIRES_YOU                               = 10301,  -- As you may remember, the test requires you to visit one of several different dungeons.
        TO_BE_QUITE_FRANK_WE_HAVE_RECEIVED_A                                    = 10302,  -- To be quite frank, we have received a large number of signatures from the Adventurers' Mutual Aid Network. Evidently, what with all the adventurers coming and going, they need some help with non-battle activities as well.
        GIVEN_THAT_THE_COMMITTEE_DELIBERATED_DAY_AND_NIGHT                      = 10303,  -- Given that, the committee deliberated day and night to come up with a solution. As a result of this grueling debacle, an executive decision was made to issue special tickets for the price of # gil.
        THE_COMMITTEE_BASED_ITS_JUDGMENT_ON_THE_IDEA                            = 10304,  -- The committee based its judgment on the idea that accumulating funds is yet another sign of a stalwart adventurer.
        AFTER_ALL_ADOULIN_IS_A_CITY_OF_MARITIME                                 = 10305,  -- After all, Adoulin is a city of maritime trade, just like our beloved Jeuno. We recognize that it welcomes business skill in all its forms, without regard to race or creed.
        AS_I_HAVE_PREVIOUSLY_MENTIONED_ISSUING_WILL_INCUR                       = 10306,  -- As I have previously mentioned, issuing % will incur a fee of # gil.
        BEGIN_FILLING_OUT_THE_PAPERWORK                                         = 10307,  -- Begin filling out the paperwork?
        PAY_FOR_THE_ISSUANCE_OF_YOUR_DOCUMENTS_NO                               = 10308,  -- Pay for the issuance of your documents? No time like the present! I need more time to think.
        ARE_YOU_SURE_2                                                          = 10309,  -- Are you sure?
        READY_FOR_ISSUANCE_YOU_BET_NOT_QUITE                                    = 10310,  -- Ready for issuance? You bet! Not quite.
        UNFORTUNATELY_YOU_DO_NOT_APPEAR_TO_HAVE_THE                             = 10311,  -- Unfortunately, you do not appear to have the required gil. Please come back once you can pay the handling fee.
