        THANKS_FOR_COMING_ALL_THIS_WAY_I_D                                      = 10393,  -- Thanks for coming all this way. I'd love to offer you some hospitality, but we'd need to get this frontier station completed first! Could you lend us a hand by signing up for a coalition assignment?
