        HOLD_YOUR_HOARDER_HARES_HERO_HEROINE_I_LOVE                             = 10596,  -- Hold your hoarder hares, hero/heroine]. I love your enthusiasm, but you're not going to learn a thing without a primer. Ahhh, here it is. Have a look-see.
