        THE_A_M_A_N_BELIEVES_THAT_LITTERING                                     = 11094,  -- The A.M.A.N. believes that littering the ground with used trinkets harms the beauty of the landscape, so we are happy to provide you with proper compensation should you trade me used orbs instead of discarding them.
        WHO_KNOWS_IF_I_M_FEELING_PARTICULARLY_GENEROUS                          = 11095,  -- Who knows? If I'm feeling particularly generous that day, you may get a fresh orb for your troubles.
        HM_YOU_WISH_TO_KNOW_MORE_ABOUT_ME                                       = 11096,  -- Hm? You wish to know more about me personally? Well, I used to be an adventurer myself, you see.
        I_MIGHT_NOT_LOOK_THE_PART_BUT_I                                         = 11097,  -- I might not look the part, but I fought on the front lines in many strange lands, earning merit points as a warrior, ninja, and various other jobs.
        HOWEVER_I_MADE_AN_IMPORTANT_DISCOVERY_ABOUT_MYSELF                      = 11098,  -- However, I made an important discovery about myself while leading that life.
        I_FOUND_THAT_BEING_FORCED_TO_DO_THINGS                                  = 11099,  -- I found that being forced to do things a certain way all in the name of efficiency kind of defeated the whole purpose of being an adventurer.
        I_FELT_THAT_EVEN_THOUGH_IT_MIGHT_NOT                                    = 11100,  -- I felt that even though it might not always be the best way, it was important to be versatile when it came to party formations, fighting styles, and the like.
        WHEN_I_THOUGHT_ABOUT_IT_LIKE_THAT_I                                     = 11101,  -- When I thought about it like that, I decided to retire and become a merchant in order to help like-minded adventurers in their journeys.
        TO_THAT_END_I_PURCHASED_ITEMS_THAT_PEOPLE                               = 11102,  -- To that end, I purchased items that people no longer needed and looked to sell them in places where they were wanted...
        HOWEVER_I_HAD_TROUBLE_MAKING_ENDS_MEET_AND                              = 11103,  -- However, I had trouble making ends meet and, as you can see from the looks of me, ended up quite poor. So, with nothing but the clothes on my back, I trudged on until I was introduced to this job by a contact from my adventurer days.
        NOW_I_M_ABLE_TO_AT_LEAST_PUT                                            = 11104,  -- Now, I'm able to at least put food on the table while still realizing my dream of helping other adventurers, so it was all worth it.
        OF_COURSE_I_M_HAPPY_IF_I_CAN                                            = 11105,  -- Of course, I'm happy if I can turn a small profit along the way too, so I'd appreciate it if you could buy some % from me as well!
        I_HAVE_RECEIVED_A_TOTAL_OF_FROM_YOU                                     = 11106,  -- I have received a total of # from you so far. Let me know if you wish to trade some of them for an orb.
        UM_I_M_SORRY_BUT_YOU_CAN_T                                              = 11107,  -- Um... I'm sorry, but you can't carry any more. Would you like to exchange some for an orb or two?
        THIS_ONE_HAS_ALREADY_BEEN_USED_PERHAPS_I                                = 11108,  -- This one has already been used. Perhaps I can offer you a free one to satiate your lust for treasures. Here you are--a freshly charged %.
        THIS_ONE_HAS_ALREADY_BEEN_USED_I_LL                                     = 11109,  -- This one has already been used. I'll give you a freebie, okay? Here. %.
        OH_THIS_ONE_HASN_T_BEEN_USED_YET                                        = 11110,  -- Oh, this one hasn't been used yet. Nothing I can do with it.
        HM_WHAT_S_THAT_YOU_RE_LOOKIN_FOR                                        = 11111,  -- Hm? What's that? You're lookin' for's some girl, are ya?
        AH_I_KNOW_THE_GIRL_YER_TALKIN_ABOUT                                     = 11112,  -- Ah, I know the girl yer talkin' about! The one who's here for the Festival of Brave Souls!
        THE_FESTIVAL_S_A_VERY_IMPORTANT_EVENT_FOR                               = 11113,  -- The festival's a very important event for us Goblins. It's been around fer ages now.
        IT_S_HELD_WHENEVER_WE_GOBLINS_ARE_IN                                    = 11114,  -- It's held whenever we Goblins are in danger or the world itself has lost all hope...
        THE_FESTIVAL_HELPS_BRING_US_A_SENSE_OF                                  = 11115,  -- The festival helps bring us a sense of calm when we feel like prayin' is our only remainin' option.
        THE_LAST_TIME_IT_WAS_HELD_WAS_OVER                                      = 11116,  -- The last time it was held was over several hundred years ago... They say there was a battle 'tween the gods of light and darkness.
        OF_COURSE_THE_REASON_WE_RE_HOLDIN_IT                                    = 11117,  -- Of course, the reason we're holdin' it again now goes without sayin'. Countless World Eater Eggs are being found across the land.
        YES_I_VE_HEARD_ALL_ABOUT_YOU_AS                                         = 11118,  -- Yes, I've heard all about you as well.
        YA_SAVED_OUR_GOBLIN_HEROES_FROM_CERTAIN_DEATH                           = 11119,  -- Ya saved our Goblin heroes from certain death on Zepwell Island, yes?
        EVEN_THOUGH_YOU_RE_NO_BEASTIE_YA_KNOW                                   = 11120,  -- Even though you're no beastie, ya know just how terrifyin' a World Eater Egg from Chaos truly is.
        THEREFORE_YOU_CAN_UNDERSTAND_THE_FEAR_ANXIETY_AND                       = 11121,  -- Therefore, you can understand the fear, anxiety, and general unease that we Goblins are feelin', right?
        IN_FACT_IT_TERRIFIES_US_BEASTIES_SO_MUCH                                = 11122,  -- In fact, it terrifies us beasties so much that many aren't even able to work. That's why we need to have this festival--to calm everyone's nerves.
        HM_YOU_WANNA_KNOW_HOW_THIS_GIRL_YER                                     = 11123,  -- Hm? You wanna know how this girl yer lookin' for's involved with the festival?
        THE_FESTIVAL_OF_BRAVE_SOULS_IS_ALWAYS_A                                 = 11124,  -- The Festival of Brave Souls is always a sad affair, so I thought it'd be good to prepare somethin' a bit more lighthearted. Ya know, to keep up wit' the times and all.
        SO_I_PUT_OUT_A_CALL_FOR_A                                               = 11125,  -- So I put out a call for a skilled entertainer and that girl showed up.
        HOWEVER_SHE_WAS_MUCH_WEAKER_THAN_I_EXPECTED                             = 11126,  -- However, she was much weaker than I expected...
